{"tid":513086,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿根廷模型玩家《只買模型不組裝》日本網友有人理解有人嫌","createTime":"2017-12-29T07:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T12:12:02.000Z","uid":75969,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"32030216d143697d58f93d3f484099000cf6d7b2","tid":513086,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6Kcp6Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6Kcp6Q.jpg&h=0081e8fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買了模型不組裝又繼續買來堆著，這種所謂的「山積」被許多模型玩家視為一種惡性循環，然而在阿根廷卻有一位玩家數十年來買了一堆模型幾乎都沒有組裝甚至根本沒有拆封過，他的經歷經過日本綜藝節目介紹之後引來日本網友兩極的看法，有人非常理解這種單純欣賞的樂趣，有人卻嫌這種行為根本不算是真正愛好模型，大家又站在哪一邊呢？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>日本綜藝節目拜訪阿根廷人迪亞哥</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6Kcp6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6Kcp6U.jpg&h=84cbe606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6Kcp6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6Kcp6Y.jpg&h=d364f349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本東京電視台的「世界！ニッポン行きたい人応援団」節目專門招待愛好日本文化的外國人前往日本實現夢想，在最新一集的預告當中出現一位41歲的阿根廷人迪亞哥引起日本網友關注&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>老爸過世才驚覺留下大筆債務！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6Kcp6g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6Kcp6g.jpg&h=4323b206&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>迪亞哥只好從小努力工作撐起家中經濟！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6KcqKk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6KcqKk.jpg&h=faa2e8f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6KcqKo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6KcqKo.jpg&h=7ee8e60f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n迪亞哥還在求學的時候就遭逢父親過世，更悲慘的是父親竟然瞞著家人欠下大筆債務，他只好休學在20歲就成為家中的經濟支柱努力工作還債，而幫助他撐過那段苦日子的是&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>滿屋子的田宮模型！！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6KcqKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6KcqKs.jpg&h=55fcc26b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6KcqKw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6KcqKw.jpg&h=d1b6cc91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSX.jpg&h=edd41a7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSY.jpg&h=217e1ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSZ.jpg&h=aff11d06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n迪亞哥從小就一位日本田宮模型（TAMIYA）的忠實粉絲，即使出社會工作要還債、要給弟妹學費還要給媽媽生活費，仍然將存下的零錢拿去買模型犒賞自己！奇怪的是&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>每一盒模型都還跟新的一樣亮晶晶！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSa.jpg&h=7756522d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSb.jpg&h=f9d955ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n迪亞哥的模型沒組裝的一部分的原因是忙於工作，另一部分是自己的堅持&hellip;&hellip;.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「我的9成模型都沒有組裝」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSc.jpg&h=35735550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>「因為憑我的技術無法完美做出田宮應有的品質」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSd.jpg&h=3fb65c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以他跟節目報名的原因就是&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「我想去日本找專家教我怎麼做」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSe.jpg&h=f31c5cd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然迪亞哥的節目還沒有確定什麼時候播出卻已經憑著預告引發話題，這種行為在日文通常稱為積みプラ（tsumipura）或山積み（yamadumi），也就是中文的「山積」，被許多模型玩家視為一種惡性循環，很容易成為夫妻吵架的導火線，也會讓模型零件在經年累月之下變質劣化導致無法組裝，因此某些日本網友就吐槽迪亞哥的行為不算是真正愛好模型，卻也有另一派網友非常理解這種單純欣賞的樂趣！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>迪亞哥只要閱讀說明書想像完成的模樣就很開心了！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSf.jpg&h=7d935b34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/78/06/qJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F78%2F06%2FqJeSoZ_bj6KcqKSg.jpg&h=b1395baa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉自:<a href=\"https://news.gamme.com.tw/1537806\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gamme.com.tw%2F1537806&d=HT%2BmosxtFQmebK13LlDikpnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=e9d440b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.gamme.com.tw/1537806</a>"},{"pid":"c8142014566da1041f4bba088e1669e82139750e","tid":513086,"uid":33864,"like":104,"dislike":0,"score":104,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:38:21.000Z","msg":"佢都話想搵人教佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36f572dbf6e2949727f793842705b09ab5c5040","tid":513086,"uid":49392,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:39:21.000Z","msg":"慘得過有咁大間屋俾佢擺"},{"pid":"7c98ed7f75822069666651ab10caa65b64c21909","tid":513086,"uid":75969,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"c8142014566da1041f4bba088e1669e82139750e","tid":513086,"uid":33864,"like":104,"dislike":0,"score":104,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:38:21.000Z","msg":"佢都話想搵人教佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"我自己都對模型有D興趣 但係驚唔識砌晒鳩咗D錢<br />\n如果真係有人肯教都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035821d6b62d3c148c04d9ed6fd47e26ea9170c0","tid":513086,"uid":1255,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:40:46.000Z","msg":"咁使唔使送撚晒比你班模型撚砌先叫愛好者"},{"pid":"4451982994497380dbac2a43aa85272e885d4e15","tid":513086,"uid":1255,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"035821d6b62d3c148c04d9ed6fd47e26ea9170c0","tid":513086,"uid":1255,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:40:46.000Z","msg":"咁使唔使送撚晒比你班模型撚砌先叫愛好者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:41:53.000Z","msg":"仲有唔通貝沙車場全部擺係度得個睇字唔渣得出街<br />\n果D有錢佬又唔係叫愛車"},{"pid":"af09d2481a3f67c813ec8e7